<h2>
    <a href="/blog/inflation-in-austria/">Inflation in Austria</a>
</h2>




<h6 class="post-meta">
    Posted by:
    
    <a href="/blog/author/christian/">christian</a>
    
    
    
    
    on 21 Apr 2020
</h6>





<a href="/blog/inflation-in-austria/">
    <img class="img-thumbnail pull-left" src="/static/media/uploads/blog/austria-cpi/.thumbnails/austria-cpi.png/austria-cpi-90x90.png">
</a>





<p><a href="http://www.statistik.at/web_en/statistics/index.html">STATISTICS AUSTRIA</a> provides economic and demographic statistical services to the state of Austria. <a href="http://www.statistik.at/web_en/statistics/Economy/Prices/consumer_price_index_cpi_hcpi/028929.html">This page</a> lists the Consumer Price Index it calculates every month according to a methodology that is updated every five years.</p>




